headline: US oil futures slip despite API inventory showing much larger drop in crude stocks
summary: Investing.com -- U.S. crude oil futures slipped from post-settlement levels Tuesday even as the American Petroleum Institute reported a much larger drop in weekly domestic crude stockpiles.
